questions.question: Who writes the Farmers' Almanac?
questions.query: PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT ?uri WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Farmers'_Almanac> dbp:editor ?uri }

questions.question: How big is the earth's diameter?
questions.query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT (( xsd:double(?radius) * 2 ) AS ?diameter) WHERE { res:Earth dbo:meanRadius ?radius }
